      <title>国际原子能机构称无人机袭击了被占领的扎波罗热核电站</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-08/iaea-says-drones-attacked-occupied-zaporizhzhia-nuclear-plant</link>
      <description><![CDATA[联合国原子能机构称，无人机自 2022 年 11 月以来首次袭击了俄罗斯占领的扎波罗热核电站，其中一架在反应堆大楼附近爆炸。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-08/iaea-says-drones-attacked-occupied-zaporizhzhia-nuclear-plant</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 08 Apr 2024 06:25:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
