      <title>澳大利亚锂矿商 Azure 批准 Rinehart-SQM 收购</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-08/australian-lithium-miner-azure-approves-rinehart-sqm-takeover</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Azure Minerals Ltd. 的股东已批准亿万富翁 Gina Rinehart 的私人公司 Hancock Prospecting Pty Ltd. 和合作伙伴 Sociedad Química y Minera de Chile 收购这家澳大利亚锂矿商。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-08/australian-lithium-miner-azure-approves-rinehart-sqm-takeover</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 08 Apr 2024 06:15:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>德国工业生产出现下一个好转信号</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-08/german-industrial-production-rises-in-further-turnaround-signal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国工业生产连续第二个月增长，支撑了欧洲最大经济体可能很快摆脱过去六个月可能经历的浅度衰退的希望。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-08/german-industrial-production-rises-in-further-turnaround-signal</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 08 Apr 2024 06:05:20 GMT</pubDate>
